09E13F8B.Line14.103C6C: You’re not with them? This note, I sent it to Jazem. He never showed. Does it mean he...he’s dead, isn’t he?

2F650410.Line28.103C6C: I...watch out! The Knights have followed!

60DCE4F8.VoiceDir14.103C6C: Hader comes to the realization that his lover, Jazem, is dead. He’s shellshocked and soft spoken.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “We are both hunted by the Cathedral. I found your note.”
